# Controlled code changes

**Gene:** `repo.engineering.controlled_changes.gen1` → `philosophy/genes/repo.engineering.controlled_changes.gen1.md`

## Do

- Direct, visible edits per file; small steps per subsystem.
- Maintained codemods in `scripts/` with README when many files share one semantic change.

## Do not

- Throwaway shell/Python one-liners that rewrite the tree outside review.
- Skip reading navigation (map/index) for non-trivial edits.
